activitiesAndInterests.activityDescription:
Our mission is to enable security teams and companies in all industries to put their complete cybersecurity operations on autopilot, allowing them to focus their limited resources on managing security rather than operating it. 

WeDoIT aims to bring sanity back to the field of cybersecurity through a fresh approach that makes protecting organizations easy and stress-free as your one stop shop. 

This is accomplished by integrating prevention and detection capabilities like: 

- Cynet 360 XDR – 24x7 MDR & SOC Services + Ransomware Guarantee
- Dark web Monitoring – Hunt and Mitigate Cyber Crimes with Real Intelligence.
- Pen Test and Attack Simulation – Simulate real attacks and use AI-driven insights to prioritize and reduce your threat exposure.
- Secure Web-Browser – Turn any browser into high secure browser
- E-Mail Security – Next-gen email security that prevents APTs, phishing, malware, ATO and BEC attacks
- Security Awareness Trainings – Interactive academy incl. final certificate
